Standard DDoS Protection is 1Gbps, but you can upgrade to 100Gbps protection plan from only €4.50 with promo code **let50off**

[**Build your VM starting from € 1,99**](https://manage.seflow.it/index.php?/cart/vpspro/&amp;step=0)

VPSPro is high performance VPS with no single points of failure. VPSPro guarantee you maximum uptime and data security. Storage Area is shared on local node and managed by our software as one virtual SAN. All disks are SSD with automatic data replication on 4 nodes shared on two datacenters. We built dedicated 2x10Ge Storage Network to guarantee that all data are replicated in real time.

**About Advanced SeFlow DDoS Protection**

SeFlow provides layers of defense through enhanced network routing, rate limiting and filtering that can be paired with advanced network-based detection and mitigation scrubbing center solutions. Our mitigation approach is informed by threat intelligence derived from visibility across our global infrastructure and data correlation. Tailored for any business and IT/security budget, our flexible managed service can detect and mitigate the threats of today to help ensure business-as-usual for employees, partners and customers.


SeFlow currently has [**nine global scrubbing centers**](http://www.seflow.net/2/index.php/en/services/vpspro/ddosprotection-2) across three continents with 4.2 Tbps of attack ingestion capacity. Special and dynamics rules was applied on all POPs router and firewall ensuring DDoS Protection for well know attacks. [See full map](http://www.seflow.net/2/index.php/en/services/vpspro/ddosprotection-2).

